==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Epidemic
<hw>Ep`i*dem"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Epidemy</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>An epidemic
