<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Anything which takes possession of the minds of
people as an epidemic does of their bodies; <as>as, an <ex>epidemic</ex>
of terror</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Epidemically</ent>⟦br⟧
